sailpoint.object

Class CertificationStatistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.CertificationStatistic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class CertificationStatistic
extends AbstractXmlObject
    Used to capture statistics about all of the open certifications that are currently owned/related to a SailPointObject such as an identity/application/group definition. See sailpoint.api.CertificationService for ways in which these are built and sent to the UI.
